To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private FractalAdaptiveMovingAverage _frama;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_frama = FRAMA(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_frama.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "fractaladaptivemovingaverage", _frama.Current.Value);
}
